(*
type TRSEnergyBoost
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
.. pascal::
  TRSEnergyBoost = type TRSConsumable;
  TRSEnergyBoostArray = array of TRSEnergyBoost;

TRSEnergyBoost is the record used in all consumables that refill energy. This includes potions, beers and certain foods.
